ProgramRunnableResourceReporter
public abstract class AbstractResourceReporter
extends com.google.common.util.concurrent.AbstractScheduledService
implements ProgramResourceReporter

Abstract implementation of a ProgramResourceReporter writes out resource metrics at a fixed rate that defaults to 60 seconds, but can be specified in the constructor.
